{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>一个迷宫由R行C列格子组成，有的格子里有障碍物，不能走；有的格子是空地，可以走。<p><p>给定一个迷宫，求从左上角走到右下角最少需要走多少步(数据保证一定能走到)。只能在水平方向或垂直方向走，不能斜着走。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"走迷宫 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出从左上角走到右下角至少要经过多少步（即至少要经过多少个空地格子）。计算步数要包括起点和终点。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行是两个整数，Ｒ和Ｃ，代表迷宫的长和宽。（ 1≤ R，C ≤ 40)<p><p>接下来是Ｒ行，每行Ｃ个字符，代表整个迷宫。<p><p>空地格子用‘.’表示，有障碍物的格子用‘#’表示。<p><p>迷宫左上角和右下角都是‘.’。<p>","examples":"<input>5 5\n..###\n#....\n#.#.#\n#.#.#\n#.#..\n</input><output>9\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1252","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}